  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA25">
<l>ārāṉu mātāṉuñ ceyya vakaliṭattai</l>
<l>yārāyn tatutirutta lāvatē cīrār</l>
<l>maṉattalaivaṉ ṟuṉpattai māṟṟiṉēṉ vāṉō</l>
<l>riṉattalaivaṉ kaṇṇaṉāl yāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When whoever is is does whatsoever, examining</l>
<l>[this] wide place, will there be accomplishing it? I have dispelled</l>
<l>the misery of the leader of [my] mind, full of excellence,</l>
<l>I, through Kaṇṇaṉ, the leader of the groups of celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
